beer.beer_description:
This beer celebrates our growing love of Hazy IPAs. It’s bright, juicy, and brimming with tropical fruit characters.

Expect a luminous yellow hue, thanks to a blend of premium malts. Hop additions in the whirlpool and late ferment supply the juice, while a persistent haze adds complexity to every sip.

The nose is packed with mango, peach and mandarin. It’ll remind you of fruit juice, just saying...

Malt: PALE, WHEAT, CARAPILS

Hops: CITRA, TAIHEKE, WAI-ITI, MOSAIC

items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 20 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 5!
